  "detailed_description": "<h1>OTHER GAMES BY STUDIO FAWN</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Fight your way through the many floors of \"The Labyrinth\" in this <strong>classic inspired top-down action adventure</strong> as you embark on a quest to save the blorb from the evil King Wego! <br><br>Along the way <strong>discover new powers</strong> ....<strong>find old friends</strong>.... and <strong>overcome the impossible odds</strong> ahead of you.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Two different game modes! <strong>Story mode</strong> AND the re-playable <strong>\"Gauntlet Mode\"</strong>!<br></li><li><strong>Dozens of unique abilities</strong> to discover!<br></li><li><strong>Over 60 levels</strong> spread across <strong>6 Labyrinth floors</strong>!<br></li><li><strong>RPG elements and equipment</strong> to unlock!<br></li><li>Part of <strong>a larger Bloom story</strong> and world!<br></li><li><strong>Eat Tofurkey!</strong><br></li><li>And<strong> much more!</strong></li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/717710/extras/d8fb89f0c414fff3e03fb199b6cb0bff.avif?t=1684193758\" width=610 height=403 /></span><br><br>Will you sneak through the hallways as fog? Become a master of the webs? Or perhaps use wind barriers to keep enemies away? It's up to you to find these powers...and decide how best to use them.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/717710/extras/0fb1b39956819f8b817e6ee76e08ea1d.poster.avif?t=1684193758\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/717710/extras/0fb1b39956819f8b817e6ee76e08ea1d.webm?t=1684193758\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/717710/extras/0fb1b39956819f8b817e6ee76e08ea1d.mp4?t=1684193758\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/717710/extras/29a9bf004898cf0bd8bb82d7d6bb5cfd.poster.avif?t=1684193758\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/717710/extras/29a9bf004898cf0bd8bb82d7d6bb5cfd.webm?t=1684193758\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/717710/extras/29a9bf004898cf0bd8bb82d7d6bb5cfd.mp4?t=1684193758\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Fight your way through the many floors of \"The Labyrinth\" in this <strong>classic inspired top-down action adventure</strong> as you embark on a quest to save the blorb from the evil King Wego! <br><br>Along the way <strong>discover new powers</strong> ....<strong>find old friends</strong>.... and <strong>overcome the impossible odds</strong> ahead of you.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Two different game modes! <strong>Story mode</strong> AND the re-playable <strong>\"Gauntlet Mode\"</strong>!<br></li><li><strong>Dozens of unique abilities</strong> to discover!<br></li><li><strong>Over 60 levels</strong> spread across <strong>6 Labyrinth floors</strong>!<br></li><li><strong>RPG elements and equipment</strong> to unlock!<br></li><li>Part of <strong>a larger Bloom story</strong> and world!<br></li><li><strong>Eat Tofurkey!</strong><br></li><li>And<strong> much more!</strong></li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/717710/extras/d8fb89f0c414fff3e03fb199b6cb0bff.avif?t=1684193758\" width=610 height=403 /></span><br><br>Will you sneak through the hallways as fog? Become a master of the webs? Or perhaps use wind barriers to keep enemies away? It's up to you to find these powers...and decide how best to use them.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/717710/extras/0fb1b39956819f8b817e6ee76e08ea1d.poster.avif?t=1684193758\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/717710/extras/0fb1b39956819f8b817e6ee76e08ea1d.webm?t=1684193758\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/717710/extras/0fb1b39956819f8b817e6ee76e08ea1d.mp4?t=1684193758\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><